  "texts": [
    "As it will be detailed in Sect. 5.4, this strategy is taken because tasks that are similar but peripheral to the focus of the forgetting process are expected to be the most affected by it.",
    "Table 4 reports the LLMs used by each of the surveyed methods.",
    "Models are sorted by their number of parameters, that differ by as much as 3 orders of magnitude (i.e., from 11 million to 30 billion parameters).",
    "LLMs are often released in various sizes to accommodate different use cases.",
    "The table enumerates the specific sizes used, separated by commas."
  ]
